ending%20its%20team%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20over%20'security%20concerns'%20for%20its%20team.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fbcci-blocks-pakistans-tit-for-tat-demand-fresh-crisis-deepens-impasse-over-champions-trophy%2Fcid%2F2068098%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BCCI%20has%20dismissed%20PCB's%20demand%2C%20saying%20a%20hybrid%20model%20can't%20be%20adopted%20for%20ICC%20events%20being%20held%20in%20India%20as%20there's%20no%20'security%20threat'%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSources%20told%20The%20Telegraph%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20BCCI%20has%20sent%20a%20clear%20message%20to%20the%20ICC%20brass%20in%20this%20regard%20leading%20to%20a%20fresh%20impasse.%20The%20BCCI's%20contention%20is%20simple%20-%20there%20is%20no%20security%20threat%20in%20India%20and%20hence%20no%20question%20of%20accepting%20such%20an%20arrangement%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20are%20scheduled%20to%20host%20multiple%20ICC%20events%20in%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20including%20the%20Women's%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202025%20and%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%202026%20jointly%20with%20Sri%20Lanka.%20The%202029%20Champions%20Trophy%20and%202031%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20are%20also%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20understood%20that%20all%20relevant%20parties%20are%20working%20towards%20finding%20an%20amicable%20solution%20to%20end%20the%20crisis%20and%20the%20ICC%20board%20will%20reconvene%20in%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20further%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20could%20also%20go%20on%20to%20lose%20its%20hosting%20rights%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20next%20year%20if%20its%20stubborn%20stance%20on%20the%20matter%20continues.%20The%20board%2C%20earlier%2C%20had%20also%20reportedly%20threatened%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20if%20the%20ICC%20decides%20to%20shift%20the%20tournament%20to%20another%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733301000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fi7360ff8_rohit-babar_625x300_20_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbcci-rejects-pcbs-hybrid-model-condition-champions-trophy-enters-fresh-deadlock-report-7169219%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BCCI%20has%20reportedly%20said%20no%20to%20accepting%20PCB's%20'conditions'%20over%20accepting%20a%20hybrid%20model%20for%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbcci-rejects-pcbs-hybrid-model-condition-champions-trophy-enters-fresh-deadlock-report-7169219%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Virat%20Kohli%20making%20a%20hundred%20scares%20me...'%3A%20Michael%20Clarke%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733300941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115966642%2Cimgsize-37638.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-australia%2Fvirat-kohli-making-a-hundred-in-1st-test-scares-me-michael-clarke-looks-ahead-to-pink-ball-test-in-adelaide%2Farticleshow%2F115966707.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli's%20impressive%20century%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20Australia%20has%20sparked%20concern%20among%20former%20Australian%20players.%20Michael%20Clarke%2C%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20expressed%20his%20apprehension%20about%20Kohli's%20return%20to%20form%2C%20predicting%20he%20will%20be%20India's%20leading%20run-scorer%20in%20the%20upcoming%20pink-ball%20Test%20in%20Adelaide%2C%20despite%20Australia's%20unbeaten%20record%20at%20the%20venue%20in%20day-night%20matches.%22%2C%22author