n%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224931%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22South%20Korean%20President%20Yoon%20Suk-Yeol%20speaks%20during%20the%20declaration%20of%20emergency%20martial%20law%20at%20the%20Presidential%20Office.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674fdd46ef9a5d904789cc04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223287%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESouth%20Korean%20President%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol%20declared%20martial%20law%20in%20a%20shock%20address%20on%20December%203.%20In%20his%20speech%2C%20Yoon%20accused%20the%20opposition%20of%20%26quot%3Banti-state%26quot%3B%20activities%20and%20for%20being%20sympathetic%20to%20North%20Korea.%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korean%20Presidential%20Office%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20join%20the%20protests%20that%20were%20forming%20outside%20the%20National%20Assembly%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20possibility%20the%20protests%20could%20turn%20violent.%20You%20could%20also%20get%20arrested%20since%20protests%20are%20illegal%20under%20martial%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20more%20and%20more%20photos%20of%20security%20forces%20descending%20on%20the%20building%20came%20in%2C%20it%20began%20to%20dawn%20on%20me%20that%20this%20situation%20couldn't%20be%20taken%20lightly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20had%20crossed%20the%20line%20when%20he%20got%20the%20military%20involved.%20What%20he%20had%20done%20posed%20a%20risk%20to%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20me%2C%20this%20was%20a%20critical%20moment%20in%20Korea's%20modern%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20I%20would%20regret%20it%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%20if%20I%20didn't%20head%20down%20to%20the%20National%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223443f1a9-eae9-4b0e-bae9-572074af032d%5C%22%3EThe%20protests%20were%20scattered%20at%20first%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Protesters%20gathering%