C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FCFQaoiqLkx%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1864159596333449666%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20days%2C%20Mr%20Badal%20has%20been%20sitting%20at%20the%20gate%20of%20Golden%20Temple%20with%20a%20spear%20in%20one%20hand%20and%20dressed%20in%20blue%20'sewadar'%20uniform.%20The%20Akali%20Dal%20leader's%20leg%20is%20in%20a%20cast%20and%20he%20is%20in%20a%20wheelchair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20around%209%20am%20today%2C%20shortly%20after%20Mr%20Badal%20had%20taken%20the%20'sewadar's'%20place%20at%20the%20Golden%20Temple%20gate.%C2%A0The%20shooter%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Narain%20Singh%20from%20Gurdaspur%20district%2C%20about%2075%20km%20from%20Amritsar.%20Visuals%20from%20the%20spot%20show%20him%20slowly%20approaching%20the%20gate.%20Then%20he%20quickly%20brings%20out%20a%20gun.%20A%20man%20standing%20near%20Mr%20Badal%20spots%20him%20in%20time%20and%20holds%20his%20hand.%20The%20gun%20goes%20off%20but%20misses%20Mr%20Badal%20and%20others%20near%20him%20and%20hits%20the%20wall.%C2%A0The%20shooter%20has%20been%20arrested%20and%20police%20are%20investigating%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20shocking%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20has%20said%20the%20promptness%20of%20the%20state%20police%20foiled%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%20to%20defame%20Punjab%20and%20Punjabis%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20police%20achieved%20great%20success%20by%20arresting%20the%20assailant%20on%20the%20spot%20with%20their%20promptness.%20I%20appreciate%20the%20promptness%20of%20the%20police%2C%20I%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20attack%20on%20Sukhbir%20Badal%20ji.%20I%20have%20issued%20strict%20instructions%20to%20the%20police%20to%20immediately%20investigate%20the%20incident%20and%20submit%20a%20report%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmritsar%20Police%20Commissioner%20Gurpreet%20Singh%20Bhullar%20said%20alert%20police%20officers%20Rishpal%20Singh%2C%20Jasbir%20and%20Parminder%20Singh%C2%A0managed%20to%20foil%20the%20attack.%20%26quot%3BNarain%20Singh%20has%20a%20criminal%20record.%20We%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20and%20the%20incident%20is%20probed%20from%20all%20angles.%20I%20appeal%20to%20people%20to%20maintain%20peace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20officer%20said%20deploying%20cops%20at%20the%20Golden%20Temple%20was%20a%20challenging%20task.%20%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20deploy%20cops%20in%20uniform%20because%20of%20religious%20feelings.%20It%20is%20difficult%20to%20frisk%20people%20too.%20We%20did%20what%20was%20possible%20and%20the%20result%20shows%20how%20prepared%20we%20were.%20I%20congratulate%20the%20officers%20for%20rising%20to%20the%20occasion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%20in%20the%20security%20establishment%2C%20Narain%20Singh%20has%20links%20with%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20group%20Babbar%20Khalsa.%20He%20is%20considered%20the%20mastermind%20of%20the%202004%20Burail%20jailbreak%20case%20in%20which%20four%20inmates%20escaped%20prison%20after%20digging%20a%2094-foot%20tunnel.%20These%20four%20prisoners%20were%20Babbar%20Khalsa%20chief%20Jagtar%20Singh%20Hawara%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Beant%20Singh's%20assassins%20Paramjit%20Singh%20Bheora%20and%20Jagtar%20Singh%20Tara%20and%20a%20murder%20convict%20Devi%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Sukhbir%20Badal%20admitted%20his%20mistakes%20before%20the%20Akal%20Takth.%20These%20mistakes%20included%20pardoning%20Dera%20Sacha%20Sauda%20chief%20Gurmeet%20Ram%20Rahim%20Singh%20in%20a%202007%20blasphemy%20case%20during%20the%20SAD%20rule.%20The%20Akal%20Takht%20pronounced%20the%20punishment%20nearly%20three%20months%20after%20he%20was%20declared%20'tankhaiya'%20(guilty%20of%20religious%20misconduct).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fqbijv708_sukhbir-badal-shooter_625x300_04_December_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20SAD%20MP%20Naresh%20Gujral%20said%20this%20attack%20shows%20criminals%20were%20roaming%20freely%20in%20Punjab%20and%20that%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20has%20broken%20down.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20that%20this%20attack%20took%20place%2C%20we%20are%20thankful%20to%20the%20Almighty%20that%20Sukhbir%20Badal%20was%20not%20harmed.%20Our%20party%20has%20been%20saying%20time%20and%20again%20that%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Punjab%20is%20deplorable.%20The%20government%20has%20failed%20on%20this%20front%20and%20nothing%20is%20being%20done.%20You%20can%20see%20an%20attack%20at%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20Golden%20Temple%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gujral%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Vijay%20Sampla%20has%20termed%20the%20attack%20unfortunate%20and%20said%20an%20attack%20on%20Golden%20Temple's%20sewadar%20amounts%20to%20an%20attack%20on%20Golden%20Temple.%C2%A0Congress%20MP%20Manish%20Tewari%20said%20Mr%20Badal%20was%20serving%20his%20sentence%20humbly.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20very%20sad.%20It%20is%20God's%20grace%20that%20he%20is%20unhurt.%20This%20should%20be%20probed%20and%20the%20guilty%20must%20be%20punished.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAman%20Arora%20from%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20said%20there%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20Punjab's%20law%20and%20order%20situation.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20one%20particular%20incident.%20Punjab%20police%20were%20alert%20and%20prepared%20to%20deal%20with%20this%20incident.%20Everything%20is%20in%20the%20control.%26quot%3B%20On%20the%20Opposition's%20criticism%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20politicise%20it%2C%20but%20if%20they%20want%2C%20I%20would%20ask%20Akalis%20what%20they%20did%20for%2010%20years%20because%20of%20which%20Sukhbir%20Badal%20has%20to%20perform%20these%20duties.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733294880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F0oiq4c7_badal-shooting_625x300_04_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-fires-at-sukhbir-singh-badal-during-his-penance-at-golden-temple-7167750%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20opened%20fire%20at%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(SAD)%20chief%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Badal%20this%20morning%20while%20he%20was%20serving%20his%20penance%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20Golden%20Temple%20in%20Amritsar.%20The%20shooter%20was%20overpowered%20by%20people%20present%20on%20the%20spot%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-fires-at-sukhbir-singh-badal-during-his-penance-at-golden-temple-7167750%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Agar%20India%2C%20Pakistan%20land%20kar%20jaati%20toh...'%20says%20Shoaib%20Akhtar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733294867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115963317%2Cimgsize-36626.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fagar-india-pakistan-land-kar-jaati-toh-says-shoaib-akhtar-on-champions-trophy%2Farticleshow%2F115961730.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shoaib%20Akhtar%20believes%20India%20is%20more%20eager%20to%20play%20in%20Pakistan%20than%20vice%20versa%2C%20emphasizing%20that%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20particularly%20keen.%20Despite%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20matches%20being%20relocated%20to%20Dubai%20for%20Indian%20teams%2C%20Akhtar%20urges%20Pakistan%20to%20adopt%20a%20positive%20stance%20towards%20future%20tournaments%20in%20Ind