0with%20Hoda%20and%20Jenna%2C%26quot%3B%20Kotb%20recalled%20how%20her%20former%20boss%20had%20made%20comments%20about%20her%20weight%20when%20she%20was%20younger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20remember%20I%20had%20just%20started%20working%20in%20a%20small%20market.%20And%20I%20played%20basketball%20in%20high%20school%2C%20so%20I%20always%20assumed%20I%20was%20in%20shape%20even%20though%2C%20literally%2C%20after%20college%20and%20stuff%2C%20I%20wasn't%2C%26quot%3B%20Kotb%20told%20her%20cohost%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjenna-bush-hager-first-daughter-katie-holmes-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJenna%20Bush%20Hager%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20remember%20my%20boss%20going%20to%20me%2C%20'Hey%2C%20Hoda%2C'%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Yeah%3F'%20He%20goes%2C%20'Hey%2C%20I%20got%20an%20idea.%20Maybe%20you%20might%20want%20to%20try%20to%20get%20on%20the%20treadmill%2C'%26quot%3B%20Kotb%20said%2C%20recalling%20his%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKotb%20says%20she%20was%20shocked%20by%20his%20comment%20because%20she%20didn't%20see%20herself%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20when%20you%20have%20a%20perception%20of%20yourself%20that%20is%20not%20the%20perception%20of%20the%20world%3F%26quot%3B%20Kotb%20said.%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20so%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'What%20are%20you%20talking%20about%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20went%20on%20to%20explain%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20don't%20fit%2C%26quot%3B%20people%20will%20%26quot%3Bwant%20you%20to%20wear%20something%20a%20certain%20way%2C%20cut%20your%20hair%20a%20certain%20way%2C%20speak%20a%20certain%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20people%20pretend%20to%20be%20someone%20they're%20not%2C%20they'll%20start%20losing%20who%20they%20really%20are%2C%20Kotb%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20are%20times%20when%20people%20do%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Bdo%20things%20to%20fit%20into%20a%20work%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp