tlers%2C%20has%20been%20a%20strong%20voice%20against%20gender%20bias%20in%20sports.%20She%20has%20earned%20medals%20in%20the%20World%20Championships%2C%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20and%20Asian%20Games.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20year%2C%20she%20became%20India's%20first%20female%20wrestler%20to%20reach%20an%20Olympic%20final%20but%20was%20disqualified%20after%20being%20100%20grams%20over%20the%20weight%20limit.%20Following%20this%2C%20Ms%20Phogat%20retired%20from%20wrestling%20and%20ventured%20into%20politics.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnKnown%20for%20speaking%20out%20against%20gender%20stereotypes%2C%20she%20led%20a%20prominent%20protest%20by%20Indian%20wrestlers%20against%20former%20Indian%20Wrestling%20Federation%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20female%20athletes%20%E2%80%93%20a%20charge%20he%20denied.%20The%20protest%20gained%20national%20attention%20when%20Ms%20Phogat%20and%20others%20were%20detained%20by%20police%20during%20a%20demonstration.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPooja%20Sharma%2C%20Performer%20Of%20Funeral%20Rites%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPooja%20Sharma%20has%20redefined%20societal%20norms%20by%20performing%20funerary%20rites%20for%20unclaimed%20bodies%20%E2%80%93%20a%20role%20traditionally%20reserved%20for%20men%20in%20Hindu%20culture%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Delhi.%20Her%20mission%20began%20after%20the%20death%20of%20her%20brother%2C%20whose%20final%20rites%20she%20had%20to%20perform%20alone.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShe%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Bright%20The%20Soul%20Foundation%20and%20in%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20Ms%20Sharma%20has%20conducted%20over%204%2C000%20last%20rites%20for%20people%20from%20various%20religions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733291280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F9j9vq19g_aruna-roy-vinesh-phogat-and-pooja-sharma_625x300_04_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbbc