%2C%20the%20fabs%20are%20%26quot%3Bdeadweight%26quot%3B%20for%20Intel%2C%20the%20Bernstein%20analysts%20wrote.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20%26quot%3Bscrapping%20them%20would%20also%20be%20fraught%20with%20difficulties%20around%20the%20product%20road%20map%2C%20outsourcing%20strategy%2C%20CHIPS%20Act%20and%20political%20navigation%2C%20etc.%20There%20don't%20seem%20to%20be%20any%20easy%20answers%20here%2C%20so%20whoever%20winds%20up%20filling%20the%20slot%20looks%20in%20for%20a%20tough%20ride%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntel's%20competitors%20and%20contemporaries%20are%20avoiding%20the%20hassle%20of%20owning%20and%20operating%20a%20fab.%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20world's%20leading%20chip%20design%20firm%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-taiwan-tsmc-jensen-huang-china-disruption-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENvidia%2C%20outsources%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0all%20its%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Its%20runner-up%2C%20AMD%2C%20experienced%20similar%20woes%20when%20it%20owned%20fabs%2C%20eventually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintel-amd-nvidia-chip-manufacturing-moores-law-fabless-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espinning%20them%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntel%20has%20also%20outsourced%20some%20chip%20manufacturing%20to%20rival%20TSMC%20in%20recent%20years%20%E2%80%94%20which%20sends%20a%20negative%20signal%20to%20the%20market%20about%20its%20own%20fabs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ffc1777c-08e0-4604-82ad-9cb83cb5fc05%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntel%20is%20getting%20CHIPS%20Act%20funding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOwnership%20of%20the%20fabs%20and%20CHIPS%20Act%20funding%20are%20highly%20intertwined.%20Intel%20must%20retain%20majority%20control%20of%20the%20foundry%20to%20continue%20receiving%20CHIPS%20Act%20funding%20and%20benefits%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.int