%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-383808%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222617%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EVolunteers%20work%20with%20partnered%20school%20students%20every%20Saturday%2C%20to%20engage%20them%20in%20activities%2C%20arts%2C%20and%20reading%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20also%20focuses%20on%20the%20use%20of%20Hindi%20and%20vernacular%20books%20to%20ensure%20cultural%20and%20linguistic%20relevance.%20These%20books%20are%20chosen%20to%20create%20a%20welcoming%20and%20fun%20learning%20environment%2C%20which%20encourages%20children%20to%20actively%20engage%20in%20the%20reading%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20is%20especially%20important%20as%20many%20of%20these%20children%20come%20from%20troubled%20homes%20to%20schools%20where%20corporal%20punishment%20is%20still%20common.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20sad%2C%20but%20the%20kind%20of%20environment%20they%20come%20from%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20environment%20they%20come%20to%20%E2%80%94%20where%20they%20are%20not%20heard%20and%20their%20opinions%20don%E2%80%99t%20matter%20%E2%80%94%20makes%20learning%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srishti%20points%20out.%20By%20creating%20a%20space%20where%20children%20are%20encouraged%20to%20explore%2C%20engage%2C%20and%20voice%20their%20opinions%2C%20SABIA%20inculcates%20a%20love%20for%20reading%20and%20learning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20world%20of%20stories%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20always%20a%20rewarding%20experience%20to%20see%20the%20students%20actually%20be%20interested%20in%20books%20and%20learning%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suman%20Mishra%2C%20supervisor%20of%20Holy%20Star%20School%20in%20Malad%2C%20Mumbai.%20%E2%80%9COur%20school%20is%20located%20in%20a%20community%20space%2C%20which%20has%20always%20been%20a%20challenge%20in%20terms%20of%20space%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20