%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%201%20Man%20%26amp%3B%201000%20WhatsApp%20Members%20Are%20Saving%20Wildlife%20in%20This%20Rajasthan%20Village%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Orans%20(a%20sacred%2C%20community%20preserved%20land)%20of%20our%20communities%20are%20like%20a%20courtyard%20of%20a%20house%2C%20where%20we%20live%20and%20exist%20with%20nature.%20Wildlife%20is%20like%20our%20children%2C%20they%20are%20our%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sharvan%20Patel%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F372524%2Fpadmaja-rathore-empowering-communities-through-wildlife-conservation-in-jawai-rajasthan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20conservationist%20from%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharvan%20(30)%20lives%20in%20Dhawa%2C%20a%20village%20near%20Jodhpur%20%E2%80%94%20a%20region%20where%20wildlife%20and%20humans%20have%20coexisted%20for%20centuries%3B%20but%20that%20delicate%20balance%20is%20increasingly%20under%20threat.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20growing%20up%2C%20I%20used%20to%20take%20my%20books%20outside%20and%20study%20in%20our%20fields.%20It%20was%20so%20common%20for%20deer%20to%20interact%20with%20people%20that%20I%E2%80%99d%20have%20to%20shoo%20them%20away%20every%20now%20and%20then.%20But%20today%2C%20if%20my%20kids%20want%20to%20see%20a%20deer%2C%20they%20have%20to%20go%20to%20a%20sanctuary%20or%20a%20zoo.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20our%20fields%20anymore%20because%20we%20have%20isolated%20these%20lands%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecies%20such%20as%20the%20blackbuck%2C%20the%20Indian%20bustard%2C%20and%20even%20wolves%20once%20roamed%20freely%20across%20the%20arid%20plains%20and%20open%20grasslands.%20Sadly%2C%20many%20of%20these%20animals%20have%20faced%20a%20drastic%20decline%20in%20numbers.%20The%20wolves%2C%20once%20ab