Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_462140547_1749964079138896_5423463430645741798_n_1080-1732544639-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382707%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20Jazz%20al%20Parque%20Festival%20in%20Bogot%C3%A1%2C%20Colombia.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20things%20I%20have%20discovered%20during%20my%20journey%20as%20a%20seeker%20of%20new%20sounds%20is%20the%20art%20of%20writing%20my%20own%20music.%20I%20have%20created%20it%20in%20small%20bits%20and%20pieces%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20a%20single%20here%20or%20there%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20have%20always%20dreamed%20of%20composing%20a%20longer%20piece%2C%20like%20a%20full-length%20album.%20Despite%20my%20aspirations%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20like%20something%20that%20would%20happen%20anytime%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20one%20of%20my%20travels%2C%20I%20met%20Michael%20League%2C%20the%20Grammy-winning%20founder%20of%20Snarky%20Puppy.%20This%20was%20about%20eight%20or%20nine%20years%20ago%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289488%2Fnew-york-best-chef-chintan-pandya-indian-food-begun-bhaja-champaran-meat-in-america%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20we%20attended%20a%20Roy%20Haynes%20concert%20at%20the%20Blue%20Note.%20Afterwards%2C%20we%20kept%20in%20touch.%20I%20showed%20him%20a%20couple%20of%20songs%20I%20had%20begun%20writing%2C%20and%20he%20was%20very%20encouraging%2C%20suggesting%20that%20I%20should%20record%20a%20full-length%20album.%20Despite%20my%20doubts%2C%20I%20wrote%20a%20couple%20of%20demos%2C%20and%20then%20the%20process%20took%20on%20its%20own%20magical%20path.%20Michael%20produced%20the%20album%2C%20which%20was%20released%20on%2010%20May%2C%202024%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDAjPpWAp78d%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDAjPpWAp78d%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDAjPpWAp78d%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Festival%20Jazz%20al%20Parque%20(%40festivaljazzalparque)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20album%20is%20a%20genre-defying%20fusion%20of%20Indian%20classical%20music%2C%20folk%2C%20and%20global%20rhythms%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20widely%20praised%20for%20its%20unique%20sound.%20It%20celebrates%20Indian%20%3Cem%3Eragas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20various%20formats%20and%20incorporates%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20folk%20and%20classical%20percussion%20and%20melodic%20instruments%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbout%2040%20musicians%20contributed%20to%20this%20record%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F81965%2Fforeigners-indian-classical-music%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproducing%20Indian%20sounds%20in%20a%20completely%20different%20context%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20had%20a%20two-week%20production%20session%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20another%20month%20in%20Spain.%20Besides%20Michael%2C%20we%20also%20had%20another%20co-producer%20on%20board%20%E2%80%94%20my%20friend%20and%20accomplished%20percussionist%20Pramat%20Kiran%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8uBJzibp-XI%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20about%20six%20years%20to%20complete%20this%20project%2C%20during%20which%20she%20also%20discovered%20her%20ability%20to%20engage%20in%20songwriting%2C%20specifically%20lyric%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20I%20had%20the%20honour%20of%20working%20with%20some%20of%20the%20most%20incredible%20musicians%20who%20are%20like%20heroes%20to%20me%2C%20alongside%20some%20of%20the%20best%20musicians%20from%20Bengaluru.%20The%20music%20on%20this%20album%20comes%20from%20their%20hearts%20and%20exemplifies%20their%20generosity%20of%20spirit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20this%20generosity%20of%20spirit%20that%20also%20defines%20Varijashree%20as%20an%20artist%2C%20bridging%20the%20gap%20between%20dif